Package com.company

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Event
    The Event class creates an event in the world.
    Game
    The Game class creates the World and a Player in the world.
    Item
    The item class allows the player to pick up and use items in the game.
    Player
    A player object represents the person playing the game.
    ReadCSV
    The ReadCSV class allows us to store all room and item data into CSV files.
    Room
    A Room is a "location" in the adventure game.
    UI
    The UI class provides the User Interface in which the player will interact with while playing the game game via input and output.
    World
    This class represents the whole world.
